Class MealEventHandler

java.lang.Object

public class MealEventHandler
extends EventHandler

The ability to create a meal post. (No longer accept replies) The ability to update a meal post. (No longer accept replies) The ability to close a meal post. (No longer accept replies) The ability complete a meal epost. (Cancel the event) The ability to accept a meal invitation. The ability to decline a meal invitation.
